<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title><%= companyName %> - Feedback Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f8fb;
            color: #003366;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #e0f0ff;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #003366;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            Feedback Request - <%= companyName %>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= fullName %></strong>,</p>

            <p>We hope you enjoyed our services. We would greatly appreciate your feedback on your recent booking with us.</p>

            <p><strong>Booking Details:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Name: <%= fullName %></li>
                <li>Email: <%= email %></li>
                <li>Phone: <%= phone %></li>
            </ul>

            <p>Please click the button below to provide your feedback:</p>
            <a href="https://protocol.btmtravel.net/feedback" class="btn" target="_blank">Give Feedback</a>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
